            <div xml:lang="nld">
                <p> 
                    <table>
                        <row>
                            <cell>2213. – <rs type="person" ref="../register/register-person.xml#rubens_jan">Jan Rubens</rs>, jaerlicx <measure type="currency" quantity="75">LXXV</measure> ₤<lb/> Opden <date when="1576-07-13">XIII<hi rend="super">en</hi> Julij anno XV<hi rend="super">c</hi>LXXVI</date> is gecompareert <rs type="person" ref="../register/register-person.xml#pypelincx_dionisius">Denys Pypelinck</rs>, heeft gepresenteert eenen
                    erfrentbrieff luydende op Meester <rs type="person" ref="../register/register-person.xml#rubens_jan">Jan
                        Rubbens</rs>, Scepen deser stadt, van <measure type="currency" quantity="75">LXXV</measure> Karolus gulden tsjaers, te quytene den penninck <measure type="currency" quantity="12">XII<hi rend="super">e</hi></measure>, in date
                        <date when="1565-06-27">XXVII Junij anno XV<hi rend="super">c</hi>LXV</date>, onder den grooten segel opt octroye van <measure type="currency">V<hi rend="super">c</hi>M</measure> ponden van <measure type="currency" quantity="40">XL</measure> groten Vlems tpont.<lb/>
                    Gereduceert vanden penninck <measure type="currency" quantity="12">XII</measure>
                    op XX<gap reason="illegible"/>XLV ₤ Artois Tachter <date when="1575-12-27">XXVII Decembris
                    LXXV</date>, <num type="cardinal" value="5">V</num> jaren: <measure type="currency" quantity="375">III<hi rend="super">c</hi>LXXV</measure> ₤,
                    afgenomen twee jaren, rest <measure type="currency" quantity="225">II<hi rend="super">c</hi>XXV</measure> ₤, compt, in <num type="cardinal" value="12">XII</num> jaren, alle jare:</cell>
                            <!-- müsste hier  eine <gap> stehen oder ist gemeint, dass die folgende Angabe rechtsbündig ist??? -->
                            <cell><measure type="currency" quantity="18">XVIII</measure> ₤ <measure type="currency" quantity="15">XV</measure> st. </cell></row></table></p></div>
                                
                         <div xml:lang="nld" type="note" rend="margin">
                             <head>Marginalie:</head>
                       <p>Nota. Hieraff eenen nieuwen schuldbrief geexpedieert te sijne ten behoeve van Meester <rs type="person" ref="../register/register-person.xml#rubens_jan">Jan Ruebens</rs>, overmits Joncker <rs type="person" ref="../register/register-person.xml#stembor_jan">Jan van Stembor</rs>, Schepen deser
                            stadt, verclaerde den ouden brief verloren te sijne. </p>
